name: Detour Live in The Buff Club
description:
Detour Live for one very special night moves up the road to THE BUFF CLUB.

Doors : 9pm

performing live will be 
SONG OF RETURN 
THERE WILL BE FIREWORKS
THE SECOND HAND MARCHING BAND
+ very special guest.

Don't expect an early night, some very special DJ's until 3am.

The night will also double as something very special for the Detour Team - we will be turning the club into a TV studio, filming everything and creating a TV pilot from the night on the next step to world domination.
